    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/d9699ab57931154052778e6eca58aac0.webp?t=1695307027\" width=192 height=31 /></span><br>Last Monarch : Prologue是一款Roguelite动作射击游戏，您将扮演末代魔王来延续魔族的生存，您将亲自出城踏上战场寻找求生之路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.poster.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.webm?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/2bed2d878fb9de723bb31704762e0016.mp4?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/edc5c8a608e6c2c2d86ebd062a0508d2.webp?t=1695307027\" width=192 height=31 /></span><br><strong>【WASD】 上下左右<br>【F键】      互动/开启<br>【LMB】    普通攻击<br>【RMB】   使用魔力屏障技能<br>【Space】 使用冲刺技能<br>【E键】     使用伙伴技能<br>【P键】     自杀<br>【TAB】    背包<br>【ESC】    选项设定</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/25c144fdf39a2cc9059cbf8b39525316.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=376 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/3e9a71ae185f66f916df21b4bb208e9a.webp?t=1695307027\" width=192 height=31 /></span><br><br><strong>1.在冒险的路上有许多道具可以获取，道具可叠加效果，增强你的攻击方式与能力【组建你最喜欢的流派】。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.poster.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.webm?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/c6bd5ed43e25b8748c0e46a7116102ae.mp4?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.poster.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.webm?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/d2751ead3298a60992144a55b1b0f12b.mp4?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2.流畅的打击感，运用你的冲刺技能闪躲一切对你的攻击，并给予反击。</strong><br><br><strong>3.冒险的路上什麽事情都可能发生，有机会遇到不同类型的房间、事件、人物，藉由触发特殊的互动，有机会让你提升能力，但也可能让你遭受诅咒。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.poster.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.webm?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/91a1b99d899adf77c028cfdb057f9c4f.mp4?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4.与女主角有着暧昧且生动的故事，他们有什麽需求，或是你想对他做些什麽呢?等待您自行发掘。</strong><br><br><strong>5.当您通关后会开启无限挑战，将会有更加随机的事情、更强大的怪物等着您。<br>【给予乐于挑战极限的玩家们】</strong><br><br><strong>6.超丰富的游戏场景，除了生动的画面外，这些场景物件不仅可以拿来当掩护，甚至有些可以直接破坏，破坏后会掉落什麽呢?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.poster.avif?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.webm?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/05b1aa29599cca68c7010c2400ca7802.mp4?t=1695307027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/b1d51b74c98a35cf161f5f6dd340c96d.webp?t=1695307027\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171220/extras/eed844a67412cc26454bb8d77b6f1146.avif?t=1695307027\" width=600 height=981 /></span>",
